OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780351871
OL,3,CPensioner arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman, 84, found dead in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FA 78-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder as investigations
OL,9,Fcontinue into a woman's death near
OL,10,FBognor Regis
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,13,Fproperty in Langley Grove in Aldwick
OL,14,Fat around 2pm yesterday to reports of
OL,15,Fconcern for the welfare of a woman.
OL,17,FOn arrival, they found the 84-year-old
OL,18,Fwoman had died.
OL,20,FHer next of kin have been informed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
