PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780351871
OL,3,CPensioner arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman, 84, found dead in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FA 78-year-old man from Aldwick was
OL,8,Farrested at the scene on suspicion of
OL,9,Fmurder, and remains in custody.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Alex
OL,12,FCampbell said: "This is a tragic loss
OL,13,Fof life and specialist detectives are
OL,14,Fworking hard to understand the full
OL,15,Fcircumstances of the situation.
OL,17,F"Officers swiftly detained a suspect,
OL,18,Fand at this point we are not looking
OL,19,Ffor anyone else in connection to the
OL,20,Fincident. There is not believed to be
OL,21,Fany wider threat to the public.
OL,26,@tD@POUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
