PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780351871
OL,3,CPensioner arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman, 84, found dead in
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,F"There will be a police presence at
OL,8,Fthe property in Langley Grove over the
OL,9,Fcoming days as we gather any evidence,
OL,10,Fand I ask neighbouring residents for
OL,11,Ftheir patience and understanding while
OL,12,Fthis work is carried out.
OL,14,F"If you have any information that you
OL,15,Ffeel could help the investigation,
OL,16,Fplease contact police online or via
OL,17,F101, quoting Operation Mayland."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@`O]
